T1  - Designing Realized Kernels to Measure the ex post Variation of Equity Prices in the Presence of Noise
AU  - Barndorff-Nielsen, Ole E.
AU  - Hansen, Peter Reinhard
AU  - Lunde, Asger
AU  - Shephard, Neil
Y1  - 2008/11/01
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/11/01
